            <h2>Saudi Arabian Airlines Cancellation policy</h2>
            <p>If you ever plan to travel through Saudi Arabian airlines, commonly known as Saudia airlines, you can book your<a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/"> flight tickets</a> without any doubt. Apart from excellent customer service, and easy flight booking procedures, they also have a hassle-free flight cancellation policy. </p>
            <p>According to the airlines, you <b>can cancel the flight booking within 24 hours of making a reservation without any cancellation fee</b>. They provide a complete refund of your ticket cost in case the booking was made a week or more prior to the departure date of your flight. However, the airline has the right to change 24 hours cancellation at any time. </p>
            <p>If you cancel a <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/saudi-arabian-airlines.aspx">Saudi Arabian Airlines flight </a>a few hours before the departure of the flight and the flight was booked not more than a week before then you will have to pay the penalty. As per the fare rule of the airlines, you will have to pay a cancellation fee of $100 to $500 if the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/saudi-arabian-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">ticket cancellation</a> request is made after 24 hours. If you cancel your flight within 24 hours from the scheduled departure of your flight, then you will have to pay a cancellation fee of $100 to $400. </p>
            <p>If the flight gets canceled due to any unavoidable reasons from the airline, then the airline will provide compensation to you to book the next subsequent flight with Saudi Arabian airlines. </p>
            <h2>FAQs</h2>
            <h3>How can I cancel my flight ticket with Saudi Arabian airlines? </h3>
            <p>You can cancel your flight ticketwith Saudi Arabian airlinesin three ways: on the official website of the airline, by calling the airline’s desk, and at the airport. </p>
            <h3>When can I make the request for the refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>You can make a request for a refund by filling out a refund request form on Saudi Arabian Airlines’ official website. The refund request takes time to be processed and can be granted within 7 to 10 working days. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>If your replacement flight delays your arrival by 2 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get compensation. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>You can check if your flight is refundable by visiting the official website of the airline and entering the ticket or document number and Saudi Arabian Airlines will display refund eligibility and information. </p>
